com.github.gwtd3.api.dsv
Interface DsvCallback<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the parsed DSV line (if no accessor is provided, the type will be DsvRow)
public interface DsvCallback<T>

When the CSV data is available, the specified callback will be invoked with the parsed rows as the argument. If an error occurs, the callback function will instead be invoked with null.

Author:
Eric Citaire
